There are no Canadians in the country
for normal reasons.

737
00:57:29,321 --> 00:57:30,868
- They'll sniff us out regardless.
- The Swedish Consul?

738
00:57:31,031 --> 00:57:34,706
They accused him of being an American at the airport.
They held him for an hour.

739
00:57:34,868 --> 00:57:37,917
We can't hold up under that.
We don't know what the hell movie people do.

740
00:57:38,080 --> 00:57:39,206
That's why I'm here.

741
00:57:39,373 --> 00:57:42,877
I'm gonna help you. I'll be with you the whole way.
This is what I do.

742
00:57:43,043 --> 00:57:45,091
Have you gotten people out
this way before?

743
