at the airport. I'm serious.

756
00:58:29,589 --> 00:58:33,514
No, no, no, this is what, the part when we say
this is so crazy it might actually work?

757
00:58:33,677 --> 00:58:35,520
Joe, I saw it in Burma.
They get people out.

758
00:58:35,679 --> 00:58:38,933
Snitches in banana republics?
