such as paper, spices...

877
01:10:05,118 --> 01:10:07,621
precious metals, all right here.

878
01:10:07,787 --> 01:10:09,004
Right this way, please.

879
01:10:14,377 --> 01:10:15,754
This way.

880
01:10:30,852 --> 01:10:32,149
- Uh, Mike?
